text: Jihad Benchlikha (born January 6, 1992) is a Moroccan professional basketball player. He currently plays for the FAR Rabat club of the Arab Club Basketball Championship and the Nationale 1, Morocco's first division. He represented Morocco's national basketball team at the 2017 AfroBasket in Tunisia and Senegal.Morocco – FIBA Afrobasket 2017, FIBA.com, Retrieved 31 August 2017. ==References== ==External links== * FIBA profile * Real GM profile * Afrobasket.com profile Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Shooting guards Category:Moroccan men's basketball players Category:People from Kenitra
